libs 1.6.1 API

Packages 
Package Description
com.amonson.config_location
A class to find configuration files using a base configuration file in /etc.
com.amonson.crypto
Stream classes that implement AES encryption/decryption.
com.amonson.data_access
An API to abstract access to data to in-memory databases.
com.amonson.factory
A class implementation to aid in the use of classes construction through a factory.
com.amonson.logger
Some helper classes and JeroMQ based publishers for the native java.util.logger Logger implementation.
com.amonson.node_monitoring
A class implementation that allows a cluster (one per node) of applications to monitor each other and send one-way messages to nodes in the cluster from other processes on nodes in the cluster (localhost access only using the included client called NodeMonitoringClient).
com.amonson.prop_store
An implementation of parsing/generating structured information like JSON or YAML.
com.amonson.redis
Some higher level classes to use the Jedis Redis implementation.
com.amonson.task_manager
Classes to manage tasks as either sub-processes or threads.
com.amonson.xdg
A class that implements a slightly modified version of the XDG specification to find/load cdonfigurations files from a filesystem.
